object.customQuery:
SELECT dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.StatSequence as StatSequence, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.TransactionNumber as TransactionNumber,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.CombinedKey as CombinedKey, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.AddDt as AddDt,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.BookDt as BookDt, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.TransactionEffectiveDt as TransactionEffectiveDt,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.AccountingDt as AccountingDt, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.WrittenPremiumAmt as WrittenPremiumAmt,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.WrittenCommissionAmt as WrittenCommissionAmt, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.AnnualStatementLineCd as AnnualStatementLineCd,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.ReinsuranceName as ReinsuranceName, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.ReinsuranceItemName as ReinsuranceItemName,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.StateCd as StateCd, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.ProductName as ProductName,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd as ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.ReinsurerCode as ReinsurerCode,
       dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.MajorPerilCd as MajorPerilCd, dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg.StateLineCd as StateLineCd
FROM
 dbo.policyreinsurancestats_stg

fields.name: v_reinsurance_Code
fields.expression:
DECODE(ReinsuranceName,
'InlandMarinePolicy','0019',
'InlandMarineEndorsement','0019',
'EquipCL',IIF(RiskStateCd='NJ' OR RiskStateCd='NY' OR RiskStateCd='IL','0015','0009'),
'PropertyCL',IIF(SUBSTR(reinsuranceitemname,1,8)='CatlinCL','0026','0070')
,'Cyber',IIF(SUBSTR(reinsuranceitemname,1,5)='Cyber','0097','0001')
,'Home',IIF(substr(reinsuranceitemname,1,11)='HomeSystems' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(ProductName))='Homeowners','0008',
IIF(reinsuranceitemname='HomeSystems' ,'0091',IIF(SUBSTR(reinsuranceitemname,1,7)='BalisPL','0091') )
)
,'Identity','0056'
,'PersonalLiab','0014'
,'Umbrella','0014'
,'PropertyPL',IIF(SUBSTR(reinsuranceitemname,1,7)='BalisPL','0001')
,'ILMine','0090'
,'HomeCyber','0029'
)

fields.name: MD5HashValue
fields.expression:
MD5('StatSequence' || to_char(in_Statsequence) || 'TransactionNumber' || to_char(transactionnumber) || 'WrittenPremiumAmt' || to_char(writtenpremiumamt) || 'WrittenCommissionAmt' || to_char(writtencommissionamt) || 'RiskStateCd' || RiskStateCd || 'StatelineCd' || statelinecd || 'AnnualStatementLineCd' || annualstatementlinecd || 'ReinsurerCode' || reinsurercode || 'ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd' || reinsurancecoveragegroupcd || 'MajorPerilCd' || majorperilcd || 'ReinsuranceName' || reinsurancename || 'ReinsuranceItemName' || reinsuranceitemname || 'ReportPeriod'  || ReportPeriod || 'AccountingDt' || to_char(accountingdt) || 'AddDt' || to_char(adddt) || 'BookDt' || to_char(bookdt) || 'TransactionEffectiveDt' || to_char(transactioneffectivedt) || 'PolicyNumber' || policynumber || 'PolicyVersion' || policyversion || 'v_reinsurance_Code' || o_ReinsuranceCode || 'CombinedKey' || combinedkey || 'ProductName' || productname
)

object.customQuery:
SELECT Risk.RiskId as RiskId, Risk.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, Risk.LocationId as LocationId FROM dbo.Risk
where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31'
order by PolicyKey
